  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening essential healthcare  in Pujehun district, SLeone</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1.	Rehabilitation of seven community health posts in Pujehun District
2.	Improved WASH facilities 
3.	Capacity building and support to strengthen DHMT monitoring and supervision of health posts .
4.	Building community ownership of the health facilities to ensure sustainability</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will strengthen health service systems and improve health outcomes across six chiefdoms in Pujehun district, benefiting over 36,000 people.</narrative>
  </description>
